[I] A implementation of the Advanced Access Content System specification

[T] libaacs is a research project to implement the Advanced Access Content
[T] System specification. This research project provides, through an
[T] open-source library, a way to understand how the AACS works. This project
[T] doesn't offer any key or certificate that could be used to decode
[T] encrypted copyrighted material.

